    <div class="fr-view">
        <h2 id="isPasted" style="text-align: center;">Our response to COVID-19 </h2><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;">At Second Harvest, the health and safety of our staff, volunteers, guests, and community partners is our top priority.  </p>
    </div>


    



